title: Low psnr on the validation set (Adobe 240 dataset)
body:
I followed all the preprocessed steps, and load the pretrained model you provived, when I fine-tune this model, I find that the ValPSNR is really lower than the paper which is 31.19.
Any suggestion would be appreciated.
